# Hoist @sentry/cli (and its platform binaries) to the top-level node_modules.
# @sentry/react-native's Xcode "Bundle React Native code and images" build phase
# resolves `@sentry/cli/package.json` from the project root. Under pnpm's default
# isolated node_modules, @sentry/cli lives nested inside .pnpm and is not resolvable
# from the root, so the bundle script aborts (MODULE_NOT_FOUND) and the iOS archive
# fails. The `[]` suffix appends to pnpm's default public-hoist-pattern (eslint/prettier).
public-hoist-pattern[]=*@sentry/cli*
